Liece is an InternetRelayChat (IRC) client for Emacs.

Get it here:

* http://www.unixuser.org/~ueno/liece/

Liece looks a bit different from the other Emacs IRC Clients, it has a specific buffer to write messages and another to receive messages, you can also write in the minibuffer and use all the key bindings it provides.

----
